135
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:50,120
Do this for thirty minutes, three times a day.

136
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:52,530
Add it to your current training menu.

137
00:08:52,530 --> 00:08:53,390
Also...

138
00:08:54,610 --> 00:08:56,640
We'll begin sparring now.

139
00:08:57,330 --> 00:09:01,270
Use Ryu the way I just taught you.
You can start out slow.

140
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:05,370
When you're on the defensive,
determine your opponent's attack power

141
00:09:05,370 --> 00:09:07,970
before defending with Ryu.

142
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:10,280
With that said...

143
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:11,280
Begin!

144
00:09:11,730 --> 00:09:13,150
I'll go first, then.

145
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:17,660
Right leg, 55 POW.

